entries.femaleVariant: Look, I know it's your big premiere, but I really can't. They're making me stay late today.
Honey, why would I lie to you?
Oh, I'm selfish? Mhm, right. What do you want from me? You want me to quit my job?!
"Not what you meant."? Well, that's what it would mean. You like that Japantown apartment, right? You think your little theater's paying for it?
Mhm... Look, I'm sorry... Hello? Hello?
